<h2></b>Starting with basic Initialization</b></h2>
<p>The first thing you will do is change the name of the blog or change the image and delete some pseudo-posts</p>
<p>Former is simple, you just delete files under _posts tab and change the contents in config.yml.</p>
<p>Next, I deleted some of the contents in _layout/home.html, and changed background img</p>
<p align="center">
<img align="center" height=400 src="home_html.png">
</p>
