<p align="center">
<img align="center" height=400 src="start.png">
</p>
<p>I am planning to put my own feature into the main page later.</p>
<hr />
<h2></b>Adding additional Link</b></h2>
<p>I would like to add additional content at top bar that links to my Github.</p>
<p>Under _includes, there is a file named &quot;navbar&quot;.html</p>
<img align="center" height=400 src="navbar_.png">
<p>Add</p>
<pre><code>
&lt;li class=&quot;nav-item&quot;&gt;
&lt;a class=&quot;nav-link&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/hslrock&quot;&gt;Github&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;

</code></pre>
<p>in amy position. The result will be:</p>
<img align="center" height=50 src="navbar.png">
<p>Next we will discuss the organizing the posts into different categories</p>
